{
  "name": "Lead-Nurture Sequence",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Lead-Nurture Sequence — 5 touches over 10 days\nWhen a lead comes in but doesn't book, this drips 5 SMS touches over 10 days so warm leads don't go cold. Stop the sequence by deactivating or adding a reply check (see note).\n\n### Setup (5 min)\n1. **Config node** → Twilio **Account SID**, your **From** number, your **booking link**.\n2. Add the **HTTP Basic Auth** credential (Account SID : Auth Token) on each *Day N* node (or set it once and copy).\n3. POST new leads to this webhook. Expected body fields: `name`, `phone`.\n4. Edit each *Day N* message to your voice. Activate.\n\nUpgrades: swap any *Day N* SMS for an **Email** node for variety; add an **IF** after each Wait that checks a 'booked' flag (Sheet/CRM) to stop nurturing once they convert. Client pays Twilio (~$0.0079/SMS). $0 to you.",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 460
      },
      "id": "note1",
      "name": "Setup Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [180, 40]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "httpMethod": "POST", "path": "nurture-lead", "responseMode": "onReceived", "options": {} },
      "id": "webhook1",
      "name": "New Lead Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [220, 480]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "keepOnlySet": false,
        "values": {
          "string": [
            { "name": "accountSid", "value": "ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx" },
            { "name": "fromNumber", "value": "+15551234567" },
            { "name": "bookingLink", "value": "https://cal.com/your-handle/intro" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "config1",
      "name": "Config — edit me",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [420, 480]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "keepOnlySet": false,
        "values": {
          "string": [
            { "name": "leadName", "value": "={{ $json.body.name }}" },
            { "name": "leadPhone", "value": "={{ $json.body.phone }}" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "set1",
      "name": "Extract Lead",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [620, 480]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ 'https://api.twilio.com/2010-04-01/Accounts/' + $('Config — edit me').item.json.accountSid + '/Messages.json' }}",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpBasicAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "form-urlencoded",
        "bodyParameters": { "parameters": [
          { "name": "To", "value": "={{ $('Extract Lead').item.json.leadPhone }}" },
          { "name": "From", "value": "={{ $('Config — edit me').item.json.fromNumber }}" },
          { "name": "Body", "value": "={{ 'Hi ' + $('Extract Lead').item.json.leadName + ', thanks for reaching out! I help local businesses stop losing leads to slow follow-up. Want to grab a quick time? ' + $('Config — edit me').item.json.bookingLink }}" }
        ] },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "http0",
      "name": "Day 0 — Welcome",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [820, 480]
    },
    { "parameters": { "amount": 1, "unit": "days" }, "id": "wait1", "name": "Wait 1 Day", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait", "typeVersion": 1, "position": [1020, 480] },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ 'https://api.twilio.com/2010-04-01/Accounts/' + $('Config — edit me').item.json.accountSid + '/Messages.json' }}",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpBasicAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "form-urlencoded",
        "bodyParameters": { "parameters": [
          { "name": "To", "value": "={{ $('Extract Lead').item.json.leadPhone }}" },
          { "name": "From", "value": "={{ $('Config — edit me').item.json.fromNumber }}" },
          { "name": "Body", "value": "={{ $('Extract Lead').item.json.leadName + ', quick proof: replying to a new lead within 5 minutes makes you ~21x more likely to win the job. Most businesses take hours. Want me to set that up for you? ' + $('Config — edit me').item.json.bookingLink }}" }
        ] },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "http1",
      "name": "Day 1 — Proof",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [1220, 480]
    },
    { "parameters": { "amount": 2, "unit": "days" }, "id": "wait2", "name": "Wait 2 Days", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait", "typeVersion": 1, "position": [1420, 480] },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ 'https://api.twilio.com/2010-04-01/Accounts/' + $('Config — edit me').item.json.accountSid + '/Messages.json' }}",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpBasicAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "form-urlencoded",
        "bodyParameters": { "parameters": [
          { "name": "To", "value": "={{ $('Extract Lead').item.json.leadPhone }}" },
          { "name": "From", "value": "={{ $('Config — edit me').item.json.fromNumber }}" },
          { "name": "Body", "value": "={{ 'Still thinking it over, ' + $('Extract Lead').item.json.leadName + '? I can install missed-call text-back + speed-to-lead for a flat fee — usually pays for itself in 2 recovered jobs. Reply \\'info\\' and I\\'ll send details.' }}" }
        ] },
        "options": {}
